# <%= @candidate.name %>

Generated: <%= Date.today.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") %>

---

## Personal Information

- **Email:** <%= @candidate.email.presence || "—" %>
- **Source:** <%= @candidate.job_source.presence&.humanize || "—" %><% if @candidate.job_source == "others" && @candidate.job_source_other.present? %> (<%= @candidate.job_source_other %>)<% end %>
- **PH Residency Confirmed:** <%= @candidate.ph_residency_confirmed? ? "Yes" : "No" %>
- **US Hours Agreement:** <%= @candidate.us_hours_agreement? ? "Yes" : "No" %>

---

## Role & Pipeline

- **Job Role:** <%= @candidate.job_role&.title || "—" %>
- **Client:** <%= @candidate.job_role&.client&.name || "—" %>
- **Pipeline Stage:** Hired
- **Hired:** <%= @candidate.hired_at&.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") || "—" %>

---

## Compensation

- **Asking Salary:** <%= @candidate.asking_salary.present? ? "USD #{@candidate.asking_salary}" : "—" %>
- **Preferred Interview Time:** <%= @candidate.preferred_interview_time.presence || "—" %>
- **Compensation Package:** <%= @candidate.compensation_package.presence || "—" %>

---

## CV Analysis

<% cv = @candidate.cv_analysis %>
<% if cv&.completed? %>
<% fb = cv.structured_feedback %>
<% reqs = Array(fb["cv_requirements_coverage"]) %>
<% adj  = fb["cv_fit_adjustments"] || {} %>
<% nh_bonus = fb["nice_to_have_bonus"]&.to_f || 0.0 %>

- **CV Fit Score:** <%= cv.cv_fit_score&.round(1) || "—" %>/10
- **Tier:** <%= cv.cv_fit_score.present? ? (cv.cv_fit_score >= 7.5 ? "Shortlist" : cv.cv_fit_score >= 5.0 ? "Borderline" : "Archive") : "—" %>

### Summary

<%= cv.summary.presence || "No summary available." %>

<% if reqs.any? %>
### Requirements Coverage

<% reqs.each do |r| %>
- **<%= r["requirement"] %>** — <%= r["coverage"]&.humanize || "—" %><% if r["evidence"].present? %>: _<%= r["evidence"] %>_<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if adj.any? %>
### Adjustments

<% adj.each do |key, val| %>
- <%= key.humanize %>: <%= val.to_f >= 0 ? "+#{val}" : val %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if nh_bonus != 0 %>
### Nice-to-Have Bonus

+<%= nh_bonus %>
<% end %>

<% else %>
_CV analysis not completed._
<% end %>

---

## Video Interview Analysis

<% va = @candidate.video_analysis %>
<% if va&.completed? %>
<% vfb = va.structured_feedback || {} %>
<% ep_dims = vfb["episode_dimensions"] || {} %>

- **Episode Score:** <%= va.episode_score&.round(1) || "—" %>/10
- **Tier:** <%= va.episode_tier || "—" %>
- **Recommendation:** <%= vfb["recommendation"].presence || "—" %>

### Summary

<%= va.summary.presence || "No summary available." %>

<% if ep_dims.any? %>
### Dimension Scores

<% dim_labels = {
  "relevance_discipline"  => "Relevance & Discipline (20%)",
  "ownership_language"    => "Ownership Language (10%)",
  "outcome_orientation"   => "Outcome Orientation (30%)",
  "adaptability_signal"   => "Adaptability Signal (25%)",
  "communication_clarity" => "Communication Clarity (15%)"
} %>
<% ep_dims.each do |key, val| %>
<% rating = val.is_a?(Hash) ? (val["rating"] || val.values.first) : val %>
- **<%= dim_labels[key] || key.humanize %>:** <%= rating&.humanize || "—" %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if vfb["decision_rationale"].present? %>
### Decision Rationale

<%= vfb["decision_rationale"] %>
<% end %>

<% flags = Array(vfb["red_flags"]) %>
<% if flags.any? %>
### Red Flags

<% flags.each do |flag| %>
<% if flag.is_a?(Hash) %>
- **<%= flag["flag"] %>**<% if flag["rationale"].present? %>: <%= flag["rationale"] %><% end %><% if flag["literal_quote"].present? %> _"<%= flag["literal_quote"] %>"_<% end %>
<% else %>
- <%= flag %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% else %>
_Video interview analysis not completed._
<% end %>

---

## Recruiter Notes

<%= @candidate.recruiter_notes.presence || "_No notes recorded._" %>

---

## Timeline

<% tl = [
  ["Applied",         @candidate.applied_at],
  ["Screened",        @candidate.screened_at],
  ["Interviewed",     @candidate.interviewed_at],
  ["Shortlisted",     @candidate.shortlisted_at],
  ["Final Interview", @candidate.final_interview_at],
  ["Hired",           @candidate.hired_at]
] %>
<% tl.each do |label, date| %>
- **<%= label %>:** <%= date ? date.strftime("%B %-d, %Y") : "—" %>
<% end %>
